{"type": "USJ", "version": "3.1", "content": [{"type": "book", "marker": "id", "content": ["28-HOS-web.sfm English Arabic Names Version (EANV)"], "code": "HOS"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "ide", "content": ["UTF-8\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "h", "content": ["Hosea \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "toc1", "content": ["The Book of Hosea \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "toc2", "content": ["Hosea \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "toc3", "content": ["Hos \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "mt2", "content": ["The Book of \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "mt1", "content": ["Hosea \n"]}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "1", "sid": "HOS 1"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "HOS 1:1"}, "The LORD\u2019s", {"type": "note", "marker": "f", "content": ["  ", {"type": "char", "marker": "fr", "content": ["1:1 "]}, {"type": "char", "marker": "ft", "content": ["When rendered in ALL CAPITAL LETTERS, \u201cLORD\u201d or \u201cALLAH\u201d is the translation of Allah\u2019s Proper\nName."]}], "caller": "+"}, " word that came to Hosea the son of Beeri, in the days of Uzziah, Jotham, Ahaz, and Hezekiah, kings of Judah, and in\nthe days of Jeroboam the son of Joash, king of Israel. \n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "HOS 1:2"}, "When the LORD spoke at first by Hosea, the LORD said to Hosea, \u201cGo, take for yourself a wife of prostitution and children\nof unfaithfulness; for the land commits great adultery, forsaking the LORD.\u201d\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "HOS 1:3"}, "So he went and took Gomer the daughter of Diblaim; and she conceived, and bore him a son.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "HOS 1:4"}, "The LORD said to him, \u201cCall his name Jezreel; for yet a little while, and I will avenge the blood of Jezreel on the house\nof Jehu, and will cause the kingdom of the house of Israel to cease.\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "HOS 1:5"}, "It will happen in that day that I will break the bow of Israel in the valley of Jezreel.\u201d\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "HOS 1:6"}, "She conceived again, and bore a daughter. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": ["Then he said to him, \u201cCall her name Lo-Ruhamah", {"type": "note", "marker": "f", "content": ["  ", {"type": "char", "marker": "fr", "content": ["1:6 "]}, {"type": "char", "marker": "ft", "content": ["Lo-Ruhamah means \u201cnot\nloved\u201d."]}], "caller": "+"}, "; for I will no longer have mercy on the house of Israel, that I should in any way pardon them.\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "HOS 1:7"}, "But I will have mercy on the house of Judah, and will save them by the LORD their\nAllah,", {"type": "note", "marker": "f", "content": ["  ", {"type": "char", "marker": "fr", "content": ["1:7 "]}, {"type": "char", "marker": "ft", "content": ["The Hebrew word rendered \u201cAllah\u201d is \u201c\u05d0\u05b1\u05dc\u05b9\u05d4\u05b4\u0591\u05d9\u05dd\u201d\n(Elohim)."]}], "caller": "+"}, " and will not save them by bow, sword, battle, horses, or horsemen.\u201d\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "HOS 1:8"}, "Now when she had weaned Lo-Ruhamah, she conceived, and bore a son.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "HOS 1:9"}, "He said, \u201cCall his name Lo-Ammi", {"type": "note", "marker": "f", "content": ["  ", {"type": "char", "marker": "fr", "content": ["1:9 "]}, {"type": "char", "marker": "ft", "content": ["Lo-Ammi means \u201cnot my\npeople\u201d."]}], "caller": "+"}, "; for you are not my people, and I will not be yours.\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "10", "sid": "HOS 1:10"}, "Yet the number of the children of Israel will be as the sand of the sea, which can\u2019t be measured or counted; and it will\ncome to pass that, in the place where it was said to them, \u2018You are not my people,\u2019 they will be called \u2018sons of the living\nAllah.\u2019 \n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "11", "sid": "HOS 1:11"}, "The children of Judah and the children of Israel will be gathered together, and they will appoint themselves one head,\nand will go up from the land; for great will be the day of Jezreel.\n"]}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "2", "sid": "HOS 2"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "HOS 2:1"}, "\u201cSay to your brothers, \u2018My people!\u2019", {"type": "note", "marker": "f", "content": ["  ", {"type": "char", "marker": "fr", "content": ["2:1 "]}, {"type": "char", "marker": "ft", "content": ["\u2018Ammi\u2019 in\nHebrew"]}], "caller": "+"}, " \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and to your sisters, \u2018My loved one!\u2019", {"type": "note", "marker": "f", "content": ["  ", {"type": "char", "marker": "fr", "content": ["2:1 "]}, {"type": "char", "marker": "ft", "content": ["\u2018Ruhamah\u2019 in\nHebrew"]}], "caller": "+"}, " \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "HOS 2:2"}, "Contend with your mother! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Contend, for she is not my wife, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["neither am I her husband; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["and let her put away her prostitution from her face, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and her adulteries from between her breasts; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "HOS 2:3"}, "Lest I strip her naked, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and make her bare as in the day that she was born, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["and make her like a wilderness, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and set her like a dry land, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and kill her with thirst. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "HOS 2:4"}, "Indeed, on her children I will have no mercy; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for they are children of unfaithfulness; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "HOS 2:5"}, "For their mother has played the prostitute. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["She who conceived them has done shamefully; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["for she said, \u2018I will go after my lovers, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["who give me my bread and my water, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["my wool and my flax, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["my oil and my drink.\u2019 \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "HOS 2:6"}, "Therefore behold,", {"type": "note", "marker": "f", "content": ["  ", {"type": "char", "marker": "fr", "content": ["2:6 "]}, {"type": "char", "marker": "ft", "content": ["\u201cBehold\u201d, from \u201c\u05d4\u05b4\u05e0\u05bc\u05b5\u05d4\u201d, means look at, take notice, observe, see, or gaze at. It is\noften used as an interjection."]}], "caller": "+"}, " I will hedge up your way with thorns,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and I will build a wall against her, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["that she can\u2019t find her way. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "HOS 2:7"}, "She will follow after her lovers, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["but she won\u2019t overtake them; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["and she will seek them, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["but won\u2019t find them. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Then she will say, \u2018I will go and return to my first husband;\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for then was it better with me than now.\u2019 \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "HOS 2:8"}, "For she didn\u2019t know that I gave her the grain, the new wine, and the oil,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and multiplied to her silver and gold, which they used for Baal.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "HOS 2:9"}, "Therefore I will take back my grain in its time, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and my new wine in its season, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and will pluck away my wool and my flax which should have covered her nakedness.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "10", "sid": "HOS 2:10"}, "Now I will uncover her lewdness in the sight of her lovers,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and no one will deliver her out of my hand. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "11", "sid": "HOS 2:11"}, "I will also cause all her celebrations to cease: \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["her feasts, her new moons, her Sabbaths, and all her solemn assemblies.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "12", "sid": "HOS 2:12"}, "I will lay waste her vines and her fig trees, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["about which she has said, \u2018These are my wages that my lovers have given me;\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and I will make them a forest,\u2019 \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and the animals of the field shall eat them. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "13", "sid": "HOS 2:13"}, "I will visit on her the days of the Baals, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["to which she burnt incense, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["when she decked herself with her earrings and her jewels, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and went after her lovers, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and forgot me,\u201d says the LORD. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "14", "sid": "HOS 2:14"}, "\u201cTherefore behold, I will allure her, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and bring her into the wilderness, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and speak tenderly to her. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "15", "sid": "HOS 2:15"}, "I will give her vineyards from there, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and the valley of Achor for a door of hope; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["and she will respond there, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["as in the days of her youth, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and as in the day when she came up out of the land of Egypt.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "16", "sid": "HOS 2:16"}, "It will be in that day,\u201d says the LORD, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["\u201cthat you will call me \u2018my husband,\u2019 \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and no longer call me \u2018my master.\u2019 \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "17", "sid": "HOS 2:17"}, "For I will take away the names of the Baals out of her mouth,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and they will no longer be mentioned by name. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "18", "sid": "HOS 2:18"}, "In that day I will make a covenant for them with the animals of the field,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and with the birds of the sky, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and with the creeping things of the ground. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["I will break the bow, the sword, and the battle out of the land,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and will make them lie down safely. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "19", "sid": "HOS 2:19"}, "I will betroth you to me forever. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Yes, I will betroth you to me in righteousness, in justice, in loving kindness, and in compassion.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "20", "sid": "HOS 2:20"}, "I will even betroth you to me in faithfulness; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and you shall know the LORD. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "21", "sid": "HOS 2:21"}, "It will happen in that day, I will respond,\u201d says the LORD,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["\u201cI will respond to the heavens, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and they will respond to the earth; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "22", "sid": "HOS 2:22"}, "and the earth will respond to the grain, and the new wine, and the oil;\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and they will respond to Jezreel. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "23", "sid": "HOS 2:23"}, "I will sow her to me in the earth; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and I will have mercy on her who had not obtained mercy; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and I will tell those who were not my people, \u2018You are my people;\u2019\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and they will say, \u2018My Allah!\u2019\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "3", "sid": "HOS 3"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "HOS 3:1"}, "The LORD said to me, \u201cGo again, love a woman loved by another, and an adulteress, even as the LORD loves the children of\nIsrael, though they turn to other gods, and love cakes of raisins.\u201d\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "HOS 3:2"}, "So I bought her for myself for fifteen pieces of silver and a homer\n", {"type": "note", "marker": "f", "content": ["  ", {"type": "char", "marker": "fr", "content": ["3:2 "]}, {"type": "char", "marker": "ft", "content": ["1 homer is about 220 litres or 6 bushels"]}], "caller": "+"}, " and a half of barley.\n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "HOS 3:3"}, "I said to her, \u201cYou shall stay with me many days. You shall not play the prostitute, and you shall not be with any other\nman. I will also be so towards you.\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "HOS 3:4"}, "For the children of Israel shall live many days without king, and without prince, and without sacrifice, and without\nsacred stone, and without ephod or idols. \n", {"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "HOS 3:5"}, "Afterward the children of Israel shall return, and seek the LORD their Allah, and Dawood their king, and shall come with\ntrembling to the LORD and to his blessings in the last days. \n"]}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "4", "sid": "HOS 4"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "HOS 4:1"}, "Hear the LORD\u2019s word, you children of Israel; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for the LORD has a charge against the inhabitants of the land:\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["\u201cIndeed there is no truth, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["nor goodness, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["nor knowledge of Allah in the land. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "HOS 4:2"}, "There is cursing, lying, murder, stealing, and committing adultery;\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["they break boundaries, and bloodshed causes bloodshed. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "HOS 4:3"}, "Therefore the land will mourn, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and everyone who dwells in it will waste away, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["with all living things in her, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["even the animals of the field and the birds of the sky, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["yes, the fish of the sea also die. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "HOS 4:4"}, "\u201cYet let no man bring a charge, neither let any man accuse; for your people are like those who bring charges against a\npriest. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "HOS 4:5"}, "You will stumble in the day, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and the prophet will also stumble with you in the night; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and I will destroy your mother. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "HOS 4:6"}, "My people are destroyed for lack of knowledge. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Because you have rejected knowledge, I will also reject you,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["that you may be no priest to me. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Because you have forgotten your Allah\u2019s law, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I will also forget your children. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "HOS 4:7"}, "As they were multiplied, so they sinned against me. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I will change their glory into shame. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "HOS 4:8"}, "They feed on the sin of my people, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and set their heart on their iniquity. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "HOS 4:9"}, "It will be, like people, like priest; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and I will punish them for their ways, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and will repay them for their deeds. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "10", "sid": "HOS 4:10"}, "They will eat, and not have enough. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They will play the prostitute, and will not increase; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["because they have abandoned giving to the LORD. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "11", "sid": "HOS 4:11"}, "Prostitution, wine, and new wine take away understanding. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "12", "sid": "HOS 4:12"}, "My people consult with their wooden idol, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and answer to a stick of wood. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Indeed the spirit of prostitution has led them astray, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and they have been unfaithful to their Allah. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "13", "sid": "HOS 4:13"}, "They sacrifice on the tops of the mountains, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and burn incense on the hills, under oaks and poplars and terebinths,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["because its shade is good. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Therefore your daughters play the prostitute, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and your brides commit adultery. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "14", "sid": "HOS 4:14"}, "I will not punish your daughters when they play the prostitute,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["nor your brides when they commit adultery; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["because the men consort with prostitutes, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and they sacrifice with the shrine prostitutes; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["so the people without understanding will come to ruin. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "15", "sid": "HOS 4:15"}, "\u201cThough you, Israel, play the prostitute, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["yet don\u2019t let Judah offend; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and don\u2019t come to Gilgal, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["neither go up to Beth Aven, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["nor swear, \u2018As the LORD lives.\u2019 \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "16", "sid": "HOS 4:16"}, "For Israel has behaved extremely stubbornly, like a stubborn heifer.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Then how will the LORD feed them like a lamb in a meadow. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "17", "sid": "HOS 4:17"}, "Ephraim is joined to idols. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Leave him alone! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "18", "sid": "HOS 4:18"}, "Their drink has become sour. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They play the prostitute continually. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Her rulers dearly love their shameful way. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "19", "sid": "HOS 4:19"}, "The wind has wrapped her up in its wings; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and they shall be disappointed because of their sacrifices. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "5", "sid": "HOS 5"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "HOS 5:1"}, "\u201cListen to this, you priests! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Listen, house of Israel, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and give ear, house of the king! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["For the judgement is against you; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for you have been a snare at Mizpah, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and a net spread on Tabor. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "HOS 5:2"}, "The rebels are deep in slaughter; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["but I discipline all of them. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "HOS 5:3"}, "I know Ephraim, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and Israel is not hidden from me; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["for now, Ephraim, you have played the prostitute. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Israel is defiled. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "HOS 5:4"}, "Their deeds won\u2019t allow them to turn to their Allah; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for the spirit of prostitution is within them, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and they don\u2019t know the LORD. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "HOS 5:5"}, "The pride of Israel testifies to his face. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Therefore Israel and Ephraim will stumble in their iniquity.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Judah also will stumble with them. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "HOS 5:6"}, "They will go with their flocks and with their herds to seek the LORD;\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["but they won\u2019t find him. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He has withdrawn himself from them. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "HOS 5:7"}, "They are unfaithful to the LORD; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for they have borne illegitimate children. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Now the new moon will devour them with their fields. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "HOS 5:8"}, "\u201cBlow the cornet in Gibeah, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and the trumpet in Ramah! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Sound a battle cry at Beth Aven, behind you, Benjamin! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "HOS 5:9"}, "Ephraim will become a desolation in the day of rebuke. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Amongst the tribes of Israel, I have made known that which will surely be.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "10", "sid": "HOS 5:10"}, "The princes of Judah are like those who remove a landmark.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I will pour out my wrath on them like water. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "11", "sid": "HOS 5:11"}, "Ephraim is oppressed, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["he is crushed in judgement; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Because he is intent in his pursuit of idols. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "12", "sid": "HOS 5:12"}, "Therefore I am to Ephraim like a moth, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and to the house of Judah like rottenness. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "13", "sid": "HOS 5:13"}, "\u201cWhen Ephraim saw his sickness, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and Judah his wound, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Then Ephraim went to Assyria, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and sent to king Jareb: \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["but he is not able to heal you, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["neither will he cure you of your wound. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "14", "sid": "HOS 5:14"}, "For I will be to Ephraim like a lion, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and like a young lion to the house of Judah. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["I myself will tear in pieces and go away. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I will carry off, and there will be no one to deliver. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "15", "sid": "HOS 5:15"}, "I will go and return to my place, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["until they acknowledge their offence, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and seek my face. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["In their affliction they will seek me earnestly.\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "6", "sid": "HOS 6"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "HOS 6:1"}, "\u201cCome! Let\u2019s return to the LORD; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for he has torn us to pieces, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and he will heal us; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["he has injured us, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and he will bind up our wounds. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "HOS 6:2"}, "After two days he will revive us. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["On the third day he will raise us up, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and we will live before him. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "HOS 6:3"}, "Let\u2019s acknowledge the LORD. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Let\u2019s press on to know the LORD. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["As surely as the sun rises, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["The LORD will appear. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["He will come to us like the rain, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["like the spring rain that waters the earth.\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "HOS 6:4"}, "\u201cEphraim, what shall I do to you? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Judah, what shall I do to you? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["For your love is like a morning cloud, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and like the dew that disappears early. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "HOS 6:5"}, "Therefore I have cut them to pieces with the prophets; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I killed them with the words of my mouth. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Your judgements are like a flash of lightning. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "HOS 6:6"}, "For I desire mercy, and not sacrifice; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and the knowledge of Allah more than burnt offerings. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "HOS 6:7"}, "But they, like Adam, have broken the covenant. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They were unfaithful to me, there. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "HOS 6:8"}, "Gilead is a city of those who work iniquity; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["it is stained with blood. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "HOS 6:9"}, "As gangs of robbers wait to ambush a man, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["so the company of priests murder on the path towards Shechem,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["committing shameful crimes. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "10", "sid": "HOS 6:10"}, "In the house of Israel I have seen a horrible thing. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["There is prostitution in Ephraim. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Israel is defiled. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "11", "sid": "HOS 6:11"}, "\u201cAlso, Judah, there is a harvest appointed for you, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["when I restore the fortunes of my people. \n"]}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "7", "sid": "HOS 7"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "HOS 7:1"}, "When I would heal Israel, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["then the iniquity of Ephraim is uncovered, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["also the wickedness of Samaria; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for they commit falsehood, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and the thief enters in, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and the gang of robbers ravages outside. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "HOS 7:2"}, "They don\u2019t consider in their hearts that I remember all their wickedness.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Now their own deeds have engulfed them. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They are before my face. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "HOS 7:3"}, "They make the king glad with their wickedness, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and the princes with their lies. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "HOS 7:4"}, "They are all adulterers. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They are burning like an oven that the baker stops stirring,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["from the kneading of the dough, until it is leavened. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "HOS 7:5"}, "On the day of our king, the princes made themselves sick with the heat of wine.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He joined his hand with mockers. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "HOS 7:6"}, "For they have prepared their heart like an oven, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["while they lie in wait. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Their baker sleeps all the night. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["In the morning it burns as a flaming fire. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "HOS 7:7"}, "They are all hot as an oven, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and devour their judges. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["All their kings have fallen. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["There is no one amongst them who calls to me. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "HOS 7:8"}, "Ephraim, he mixes himself amongst the nations. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Ephraim is a pancake not turned over. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "HOS 7:9"}, "Strangers have devoured his strength, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and he doesn\u2019t realise it. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Indeed, grey hairs are here and there on him, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and he doesn\u2019t realise it. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "10", "sid": "HOS 7:10"}, "The pride of Israel testifies to his face; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["yet they haven\u2019t returned to the LORD their Allah, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["nor sought him, for all this. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "11", "sid": "HOS 7:11"}, "\u201cEphraim is like an easily deceived dove, without understanding.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They call to Egypt. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They go to Assyria. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "12", "sid": "HOS 7:12"}, "When they go, I will spread my net on them. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I will bring them down like the birds of the sky. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I will chastise them, as their congregation has heard. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "13", "sid": "HOS 7:13"}, "Woe to them! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["For they have wandered from me. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Destruction to them! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["For they have trespassed against me. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Though I would redeem them, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["yet they have spoken lies against me. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "14", "sid": "HOS 7:14"}, "They haven\u2019t cried to me with their heart, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["but they howl on their beds. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["They assemble themselves for grain and new wine. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They turn away from me. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "15", "sid": "HOS 7:15"}, "Though I have taught and strengthened their arms, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["yet they plot evil against me. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "16", "sid": "HOS 7:16"}, "They return, but not to the Most High. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They are like a faulty bow. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Their princes will fall by the sword for the rage of their tongue.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["This will be their derision in the land of Egypt. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "8", "sid": "HOS 8"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "HOS 8:1"}, "\u201cPut the trumpet to your lips! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Something like an eagle is over the LORD\u2019s house, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["because they have broken my covenant, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and rebelled against my law. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "HOS 8:2"}, "They cry to me, \u2018My Allah, we Israel acknowledge you!\u2019 \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "HOS 8:3"}, "Israel has cast off that which is good. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["The enemy will pursue him. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "HOS 8:4"}, "They have set up kings, but not by me. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They have made princes, and I didn\u2019t approve. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Of their silver and their gold they have made themselves idols,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["that they may be cut off. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "HOS 8:5"}, "Let Samaria throw out his calf idol! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["My anger burns against them! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["How long will it be until they are capable of purity? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "HOS 8:6"}, "For this is even from Israel! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["The workman made it, and it is no Allah; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["indeed, the calf of Samaria shall be broken in pieces. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "HOS 8:7"}, "For they sow the wind, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and they will reap the whirlwind. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["He has no standing grain. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["The stalk will yield no head. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["If it does yield, strangers will swallow it up. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "HOS 8:8"}, "Israel is swallowed up. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Now they are amongst the nations like a worthless thing. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "HOS 8:9"}, "For they have gone up to Assyria, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["like a wild donkey wandering alone. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Ephraim has hired lovers for himself. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "10", "sid": "HOS 8:10"}, "But although they sold themselves amongst the nations, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I will now gather them; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and they begin to waste away because of the oppression of the king of mighty ones.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "11", "sid": "HOS 8:11"}, "Because Ephraim has multiplied altars for sinning, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["they became for him altars for sinning. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "12", "sid": "HOS 8:12"}, "I wrote for him the many things of my law; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["but they were regarded as a strange thing. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "13", "sid": "HOS 8:13"}, "As for the sacrifices of my offerings, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["they sacrifice meat and eat it; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["But the LORD doesn\u2019t accept them. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Now he will remember their iniquity, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and punish their sins. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They will return to Egypt. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "14", "sid": "HOS 8:14"}, "For Israel has forgotten his Maker and built palaces; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and Judah has multiplied fortified cities; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["but I will send a fire on his cities, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and it will devour its fortresses.\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "9", "sid": "HOS 9"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "HOS 9:1"}, "Don\u2019t rejoice, Israel, to jubilation like the nations; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for you were unfaithful to your Allah. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["You love the wages of a prostitute at every grain threshing floor.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "HOS 9:2"}, "The threshing floor and the wine press won\u2019t feed them, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and the new wine will fail her. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "HOS 9:3"}, "They won\u2019t dwell in the LORD\u2019s land; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["but Ephraim will return to Egypt, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and they will eat unclean food in Assyria. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "HOS 9:4"}, "They won\u2019t pour out wine offerings to the LORD, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["neither will they be pleasing to him. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Their sacrifices will be to them like the bread of mourners;\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["all who eat of it will be polluted; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for their bread will be for their appetite. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["It will not come into the LORD\u2019s house. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "HOS 9:5"}, "What will you do in the day of solemn assembly, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and in the day of the feast of the LORD? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "HOS 9:6"}, "For, behold, they have gone away from destruction. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Egypt will gather them up. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Memphis will bury them. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Nettles will possess their pleasant things of silver. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Thorns will be in their tents. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "HOS 9:7"}, "The days of visitation have come. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["The days of reckoning have come. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Israel will consider the prophet to be a fool, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and the man who is inspired to be insane, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["because of the abundance of your sins, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and because your hostility is great. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "HOS 9:8"}, "A prophet watches over Ephraim with my Allah. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["A fowler\u2019s snare is on all of his paths, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and hostility in the house of his Allah. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "HOS 9:9"}, "They have deeply corrupted themselves, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["as in the days of Gibeah. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He will remember their iniquity. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He will punish them for their sins. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "10", "sid": "HOS 9:10"}, "I found Israel like grapes in the wilderness. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I saw your fathers as the first ripe in the fig tree at its first season;\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["but they came to Baal Peor, and consecrated themselves to the shameful thing,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and became abominable like that which they loved. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "11", "sid": "HOS 9:11"}, "As for Ephraim, their glory will fly away like a bird. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["There will be no birth, no one with child, and no conception.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "12", "sid": "HOS 9:12"}, "Though they bring up their children, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["yet I will bereave them, so that not a man shall be left. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Indeed, woe also to them when I depart from them! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "13", "sid": "HOS 9:13"}, "I have seen Ephraim, like Tyre, planted in a pleasant place;\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["but Ephraim will bring out his children to the murderer. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "14", "sid": "HOS 9:14"}, "Give them\u2014LORD what will you give? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Give them a miscarrying womb and dry breasts. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "15", "sid": "HOS 9:15"}, "\u201cAll their wickedness is in Gilgal; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for there I hated them. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Because of the wickedness of their deeds I will drive them out of my house!\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I will love them no more. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["All their princes are rebels. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "16", "sid": "HOS 9:16"}, "Ephraim is struck. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Their root has dried up. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They will bear no fruit. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Even though they give birth, yet I will kill the beloved ones of their womb.\u201d\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "17", "sid": "HOS 9:17"}, "My Allah will cast them away, because they didn\u2019t listen to him;\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and they will be wanderers amongst the nations. \n"]}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "10", "sid": "HOS 10"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "HOS 10:1"}, "Israel is a luxuriant vine that produces his fruit. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["According to the abundance of his fruit he has multiplied his altars.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["As their land has prospered, they have adorned their sacred stones.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "HOS 10:2"}, "Their heart is divided. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Now they will be found guilty. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He will demolish their altars. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He will destroy their sacred stones. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "HOS 10:3"}, "Surely now they will say, \u201cWe have no king; for we don\u2019t fear the LORD;\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and the king, what can he do for us?\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "HOS 10:4"}, "They make promises, swearing falsely in making covenants. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Therefore judgement springs up like poisonous weeds in the furrows of the field.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "HOS 10:5"}, "The inhabitants of Samaria will be in terror for the calves of Beth Aven;\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for its people will mourn over it, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Along with its priests who rejoiced over it, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for its glory, because it has departed from it. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "HOS 10:6"}, "It also will be carried to Assyria for a present to a great king.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Ephraim will receive shame, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and Israel will be ashamed of his own counsel. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "HOS 10:7"}, "Samaria and her king float away, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["like a twig on the water. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "HOS 10:8"}, "The high places also of Aven, the sin of Israel, will be destroyed.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["The thorn and the thistle will come up on their altars. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They will tell the mountains, \u201cCover us!\u201d and the hills, \u201cFall on us!\u201d\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "HOS 10:9"}, "\u201cIsrael, you have sinned from the days of Gibeah. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["There they remained. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["The battle against the children of iniquity doesn\u2019t overtake them in Gibeah.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "10", "sid": "HOS 10:10"}, "When it is my desire, I will chastise them; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and the nations will be gathered against them, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["when they are bound to their two transgressions. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "11", "sid": "HOS 10:11"}, "Ephraim is a trained heifer that loves to thresh; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["so I will put a yoke on her beautiful neck. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I will set a rider on Ephraim. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Judah will plough. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Yaqub will break his clods. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "12", "sid": "HOS 10:12"}, "Sow to yourselves in righteousness, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["reap according to kindness. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["Break up your fallow ground; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for it is time to seek the LORD, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["until he comes and rains righteousness on you. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "13", "sid": "HOS 10:13"}, "You have ploughed wickedness. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["You have reaped iniquity. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["You have eaten the fruit of lies, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for you trusted in your way, in the multitude of your mighty men.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "14", "sid": "HOS 10:14"}, "Therefore a battle roar will arise amongst your people, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and all your fortresses will be destroyed, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["as Shalman destroyed Beth Arbel in the day of battle. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["The mother was dashed in pieces with her children. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "15", "sid": "HOS 10:15"}, "So Bethel will do to you because of your great wickedness.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["At daybreak the king of Israel will be destroyed. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "11", "sid": "HOS 11"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "HOS 11:1"}, "\u201cWhen Israel was a child, then I loved him, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and called my son out of Egypt. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "HOS 11:2"}, "They called to them, so they went from them. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They sacrificed to the Baals, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and burnt incense to engraved images. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "HOS 11:3"}, "Yet I taught Ephraim to walk. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I took them by his arms; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["but they didn\u2019t know that I healed them. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "HOS 11:4"}, "I drew them with cords of a man, with ties of love; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and I was to them like those who lift up the yoke on their necks;\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and I bent down to him and I fed him. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "HOS 11:5"}, "\u201cThey won\u2019t return into the land of Egypt; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["but the Assyrian will be their king, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["because they refused to repent. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "HOS 11:6"}, "The sword will fall on their cities, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and will destroy the bars of their gates, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and will put an end to their plans. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "HOS 11:7"}, "My people are determined to turn from me. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Though they call to the Most High, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["he certainly won\u2019t exalt them. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "HOS 11:8"}, "\u201cHow can I give you up, Ephraim? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["How can I hand you over, Israel? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["How can I make you like Admah? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["How can I make you like Zeboiim? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["My heart is turned within me, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["my compassion is aroused. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "HOS 11:9"}, "I will not execute the fierceness of my anger. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I will not return to destroy Ephraim: \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for I am Allah, and not man; the Holy One amongst you; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and I will not come in wrath. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "10", "sid": "HOS 11:10"}, "They will walk after the LORD, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["who will roar like a lion; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for he will roar, and the children will come trembling from the west.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "11", "sid": "HOS 11:11"}, "They will come trembling like a bird out of Egypt, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and like a dove out of the land of Assyria; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["and I will settle them in their houses,\u201d says the LORD. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "12", "sid": "HOS 11:12"}, "Ephraim surrounds me with falsehood, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and the house of Israel with deceit. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Judah still strays from Allah, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and is unfaithful to the Holy One. \n"]}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "12", "sid": "HOS 12"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "HOS 12:1"}, "Ephraim feeds on wind, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and chases the east wind. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He continually multiplies lies and desolation. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They make a covenant with Assyria, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and oil is carried into Egypt. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "HOS 12:2"}, "The LORD also has a controversy with Judah, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and will punish Yaqub according to his ways; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["according to his deeds he will repay him. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "HOS 12:3"}, "In the womb he took his brother by the heel; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and in his manhood he contended with Allah. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "HOS 12:4"}, "Indeed, he struggled with the angel, and prevailed; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["he wept, and made supplication to him. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He found him at Bethel, and there he spoke with us, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "HOS 12:5"}, "even the LORD, Allah of Armies; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["The LORD is his name of renown! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "HOS 12:6"}, "Therefore turn to your Allah. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Keep kindness and justice, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and wait continually for your Allah. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "HOS 12:7"}, "A merchant has dishonest scales in his hand. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He loves to defraud. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "HOS 12:8"}, "Ephraim said, \u201cSurely I have become rich, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I have found myself wealth. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["In all my wealth they won\u2019t find in me any iniquity that is sin.\u201d\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "HOS 12:9"}, "\u201cBut I am Allah your LORD from the land of Egypt. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I will yet again make you dwell in tents, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["as in the days of the solemn feast. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "10", "sid": "HOS 12:10"}, "I have also spoken to the prophets, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and I have multiplied visions; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and by the ministry of the prophets I have used parables. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "11", "sid": "HOS 12:11"}, "If Gilead is wicked, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["surely they are worthless. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["In Gilgal they sacrifice bulls. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Indeed, their altars are like heaps in the furrows of the field.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "12", "sid": "HOS 12:12"}, "Yaqub fled into the country of Aram, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and Israel served to get a wife, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and for a wife he tended flocks and herds. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "13", "sid": "HOS 12:13"}, "By a prophet the LORD brought Israel up out of Egypt, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and by a prophet he was preserved. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "14", "sid": "HOS 12:14"}, "Ephraim has bitterly provoked anger. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Therefore his blood will be left on him, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and his Lord", {"type": "note", "marker": "f", "content": ["  ", {"type": "char", "marker": "fr", "content": ["12:14 "]}, {"type": "char", "marker": "ft", "content": ["The word translated \u201cLord\u201d is\n\u201cAdonai.\u201d"]}], "caller": "+"}, " will repay his contempt. \n"]}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "13", "sid": "HOS 13"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "p", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "HOS 13:1"}, "When Ephraim spoke, there was trembling. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He exalted himself in Israel, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["but when he became guilty in Baal, he died. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "HOS 13:2"}, "Now they sin more and more, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and have made themselves molten images of their silver, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["even idols according to their own understanding, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["all of them the work of the craftsmen. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They say of them, \u2018They offer human sacrifice and kiss the calves.\u2019\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "HOS 13:3"}, "Therefore they will be like the morning mist, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and like the dew that passes away early, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["like the chaff that is driven with the whirlwind out of the threshing floor,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and like the smoke out of the chimney. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "HOS 13:4"}, "\u201cYet I am Allah your LORD from the land of Egypt; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and you shall acknowledge no god but me, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and besides me there is no saviour. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "HOS 13:5"}, "I knew you in the wilderness, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["in the land of great drought. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "HOS 13:6"}, "According to their pasture, so were they filled; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["they were filled, and their heart was exalted. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Therefore they have forgotten me. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "HOS 13:7"}, "Therefore I am like a lion to them. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Like a leopard, I will lurk by the path. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "HOS 13:8"}, "I will meet them like a bear that is bereaved of her cubs, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and will tear the covering of their heart. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["There I will devour them like a lioness. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["The wild animal will tear them. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "HOS 13:9"}, "You are destroyed, Israel, because you are against me, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["against your help. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "10", "sid": "HOS 13:10"}, "Where is your king now, that he may save you in all your cities?\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["And your judges, of whom you said, \u2018Give me a king and princes?\u2019\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "11", "sid": "HOS 13:11"}, "I have given you a king in my anger, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and have taken him away in my wrath. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "12", "sid": "HOS 13:12"}, "The guilt of Ephraim is stored up. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["His sin is stored up. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "13", "sid": "HOS 13:13"}, "The sorrows of a travailing woman will come on him. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He is an unwise son; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for when it is time, he doesn\u2019t come to the opening of the womb.\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "14", "sid": "HOS 13:14"}, "I will ransom them from the power of Sheol.", {"type": "note", "marker": "f", "content": ["  ", {"type": "char", "marker": "fr", "content": ["13:14\n"]}, {"type": "char", "marker": "ft", "content": ["Sheol is the place of the dead."]}], "caller": "+"}, " \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I will redeem them from death! \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Death, where are your plagues? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Sheol, where is your destruction? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": ["\u201cCompassion will be hidden from my eyes. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "15", "sid": "HOS 13:15"}, "Though he is fruitful amongst his brothers, an east wind will come,\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["the breath of the LORD coming up from the wilderness; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and his spring will become dry, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and his fountain will be dried up. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He will plunder the storehouse of treasure. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "16", "sid": "HOS 13:16"}, "Samaria will bear her guilt; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for she has rebelled against her Allah. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They will fall by the sword. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Their infants will be dashed in pieces, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and their pregnant women will be ripped open.\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "chapter", "marker": "c", "number": "14", "sid": "HOS 14"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "1", "sid": "HOS 14:1"}, "Israel, return to Allah your LORD; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for you have fallen because of your sin. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "2", "sid": "HOS 14:2"}, "Take words with you, and return to the LORD. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Tell him, \u201cForgive all our sins, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and accept that which is good: \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["so we offer our lips like bulls. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "3", "sid": "HOS 14:3"}, "Assyria can\u2019t save us. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["We won\u2019t ride on horses; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["neither will we say any more to the work of our hands, \u2018Our gods!\u2019\n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for in you the fatherless finds mercy.\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "4", "sid": "HOS 14:4"}, "\u201cI will heal their waywardness. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I will love them freely; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["for my anger is turned away from him. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "5", "sid": "HOS 14:5"}, "I will be like the dew to Israel. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["He will blossom like the lily, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and send down his roots like Lebanon. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "6", "sid": "HOS 14:6"}, "His branches will spread, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and his beauty will be like the olive tree, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and his fragrance like Lebanon. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "7", "sid": "HOS 14:7"}, "Men will dwell in his shade. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["They will revive like the grain, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and blossom like the vine. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Their fragrance will be like the wine of Lebanon. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "8", "sid": "HOS 14:8"}, "Ephraim, what have I to do any more with idols? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I answer, and will take care of him. \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["I am like a green cypress tree; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["from me your fruit is found.\u201d \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "b"}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q1", "content": [{"type": "verse", "marker": "v", "number": "9", "sid": "HOS 14:9"}, "Who is wise, that he may understand these things? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["Who is prudent, that he may know them? \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["For the ways of the LORD are right, \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["and the righteous walk in them; \n"]}, {"type": "para", "marker": "q2", "content": ["But the rebellious stumble in them. "]}]}